### Get list of unpaid check-ins (PaymentDate = NULL)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/check-in/unpaid
Content-Type: application/json

### Search unpaid check-ins by customer name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/check-in/unpaid/search?q=Michael
Content-Type: application/json

### Search unpaid check-ins by room name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/check-in/unpaid/search?q=101
Content-Type: application/json

### Search unpaid check-ins - empty query (should return error)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/check-in/unpaid/search?q=
Content-Type: application/json
